Show logs for a given running pod / deployment by short name.

Usage:
  stack logs <component> [flags]

Flags:
  -f, --follow   follow (stream) logs as they happen
  -h, --help     help for logs

Global Flags:
      --config string              config file (default is $HOME/.{{name of project}}.yaml)
  -r, --project_directory string   set the project directory for stack command (default ".")
